data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in Frenship ISD, just blocks from Oakridge Elementary.  This home offers a large living room with brand new vinyl plank floors and is open to the kitchen and dining spaces. The kitchen offers a large breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, walk in pantry and beautiful stained cabinets.  The primary bedroom is isolated and HUGE!  It has double vanities and a large wrap around walk in closet.  The home has recently been painted throughout and a brand new roof was just installed.  The large backyard has a 7 foot board on board fence and is perfect for a pool, playscape or entertaining.  This home is a must see in person!  Schedule your showing today!
